<!-- more -->
之前spark1.6.0时，累加器的定义及使用方式为：
```
Accumulator<Integer> accum = sc.accumulator(0);
sc.parallelize(Arrays.asList(1, 2, 3, 4)).foreach(x -> accum.add(x));
// ...
// 10/09/29 18:41:08 INFO SparkContext: Tasks finished in 0.317106 s
